<h3>API Requests:</h3>
<pre>
*listing comments
 url: http://servicoapp.cloudapp.net/comments
 method: GET
 body : not needed

*Comments listing photos
 url: http://servicoapp.cloudapp.net/comments/commentsphoto/:id_photo
 method: GET
 body : not needed

*Retrieving Comment detail
 url: http://servicoapp.cloudapp.net/comments/:id
 method: GET
 body : not needed

*creating comments
url: http://servicoapp.cloudapp.net/comments
method: Post
Body : It can be json

NOTE: attributes required=> id_photo, name, title, body

*Updating comment
url: http://servicoapp.cloudapp.net/comments/:id
method: PUT
Body : It can be json

*Deleting comment
url: http://servicoapp.cloudapp.net/comments/:id
method: DELETE
body : not needed

</pre>